OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774905063
OL,3,CWoman sentenced for attacking man with
OL,4,Ccerebral palsy at cashpoint
OL,6,FA woman has been sentenced after she
OL,7,Fknocked a 'vulnerable man' with
OL,8,Fcerebral palsy to the ground and stole
OL,9,Fhis bank card in Brighton.
OL,11,FOn Monday 27 October, 2025, a man in
OL,12,Fhis 30s was using a cashpoint in St
OL,13,FJames's Street when he was approached
OL,14,Fand assaulted by Aji Sinera after she
OL,15,Fhad asked him for money.
OL,17,FThe victim was knocked to the ground
OL,18,Fduring a struggle to take his wallet.
OL,19,FThe 30-year-old fled the scene with
OL,20,Fhis bank card and went on to use it in
OL,21,Fnearby shops.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
