PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774905063
OL,3,CWoman sentenced for attacking man with
OL,4,Ccerebral palsy at cashpoint
OL,6,FSussex Police say: "On CCTV she was
OL,7,Fseen calmly buying takeaway food with
OL,8,Fthe stolen card and also attempting to
OL,9,Fmake further transactions."
OL,11,FOfficers responded to the robbery
OL,12,Freport, and enquiries led to Sinera
OL,13,Fbeing arrested.
OL,15,FShe was charged with three counts of
OL,16,Ffraud by false representation and with
OL,17,Frobbery.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
