PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774905063
OL,3,CWoman sentenced for attacking man with
OL,4,Ccerebral palsy at cashpoint
OL,6,FShe appeared at Brighton Magistrates'
OL,7,FCourt and was remanded in custody.
OL,8,FFollowing a guilty plea during a
OL,9,Fhearing in November, Sinera was
OL,10,Fremanded back into custody to await
OL,11,Fher sentencing.
OL,13,FOn 19 March, she appeared at Lewes
OL,14,FCrown Court and was sentenced to 18
OL,15,Fmonths in prison, suspended for two
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
